'''Dyemma Reel''' was a [[Human/Legends|Human]] [[Gender/Legends|female]] [[Homeworld/Legends|native]] [[Coruscanti/Legends|to]]<ref name="DB" /> the [[Planet/Legends|planet]]<ref name="VD">''[[Star Wars: Attack of the Clones: The Visual Dictionary]]''</ref> [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]]<ref name="DB" /> who participated in<ref name="Rouges">{{InsiderCite|136|Rogues Gallery|Rogues Gallery: A Night at the Outlander Club}}</ref> their homeworld's<ref name="DB" /> party scene.<ref name="Rouges" /> Reel, who was a bachelorette,<ref name="Ladies">{{SWArchive|url=episode-ii/explore/attack/2002/06/imageattack20020621.html|series=Image Attack|text=Ladies of the Outlander}}</ref> was in attendance at the [[Outlander Club/Legends|Outlander Club]] on Coruscant when [[Anakin Skywalker/Legends|Anakin Skywalker]] and [[Obi-Wan Kenobi/Legends|Obi-Wan Kenobi]] tracked and attacked the [[Bounty hunter/Legends|bounty hunter]] [[Zam Wesell/Legends|Zam Wesell]] there.

